                    <div style="background: #f0f8ff; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 20px;">
                        <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #667eea;">💡 优化建议</div>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8;">
                            <li>建议合并采购陶瓷电容156个，可获得批量折扣15%</li>
                            <li>贴片电阻可统一供应商，减少管理成本</li>
