                    <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #f39c12;">⚠️ 价格预警</div>
                    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li><strong>MAX30102</strong> 价格上涨7%，建议尽快采购或寻找替代方案</li>
